A comfortable 90 degree jacuzzi, in the winter this natural caldera is a welcoming respite from the snow outside and is the crowning jewel of Homestead Resort, which was built around it. I‚Äôm a little embarrassed that I was vain enough to pose miserably for a few seconds to get this picture before scrambling to get in the water . The air in there felt like a freezer to this LA native and I thought my bewbz were gonna fall off. *
*

An honorable mention needs to be inserted here for John, who let me use his flip flops since I forgot to pack mine for the trip.
